    <h3 id="wallet-security">Wallet Security</h3>

<p>We use unique per-customer, per-loan multi-signature P2SH addresses for all collateral held in vaults. We use hierarchical deterministic (HD) hardware wallets to store our private keys on hardware devices and we use well-tested, industry-standard open-source software to author and audit our transactions.</p>

